  "postName": "2005-09-26-21-headphone-salute",
  "html": "<p>This is too good to pass up sharing:  At my new job, we sit in an open floor plan with head-height walls behind bench-like workspaces.  Since we don&#39;t all sit in offices, the preferred mode of privacy is the use of headphones.  </p>\n<p>Today, the Director of Engineering walked through my neighborhood looking for someone.  He said something that I couldn&#39;t hear through headphones, so I pulled mine off—as did, apparently, most everyone else nearby.  Chuckling, he announced he&#39;d been talking to himself (a frequent occurrence) but that he appreciated the headphones doffed in his honor.  </p>\n<p>Before striding off, he said, &quot;It&#39;s like a modern kind of salute, shows <em>respect</em>, I like it.&quot;</p>\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments archived-comments\"><h3>Archived Comments</h3>\n<ul class=\"comments\">\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091005\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=38bd97b8b78bb0926fc0916da9c90641&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"\">MichaelBrianBentley</a>\n</div>\n<a href=\"#comment-221091005\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T21:47:29\">2005-09-26T21:47:29</time></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"content\"><p>Headphones make my ears itch in seconds. I haven't found a set that do the job and don't drive me crazy.</p></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091006\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://dean.edwards.name/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=b33181b8e12bd10dfa373acc8af37cbb&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://dean.edwards.name/\">Dean Edwards</a>\n</div>\n<a href=\"#comment-221091006\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T23:51:42\">2005-09-26T23:51:42</time></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"content\"><p>You work in Hell.</p></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091008\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://www.decafbad.com\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2377f34a68801b861c3e54e1301f0dce&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://www.decafbad.com\">l.m.orchard</a>\n</div>\n<a href=\"#comment-221091008\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T23:59:38\">2005-09-26T23:59:38</time></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"content\"><p>Bah, this guy's not <em>really</em> a drill sargeant or anything.  Also, I actually like not having a door and walls—at least so far.</p></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091009\">\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<div class=\"author\">\n<a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://joga.be\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=8e9f4a1fa29a0923f59f3037bbaa824e&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\n<a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \nhref=\"http://joga.be\">Aneel</a>\n</div>\n<a href=\"#comment-221091009\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-28T19:12:08\">2005-09-28T19:12:08</time></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"content\"><p>That's <em>fantastic</em>.</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
  "body": "This is too good to pass up sharing:  At my new job, we sit in an open floor plan with head-height walls behind bench-like workspaces.  Since we don't all sit in offices, the preferred mode of privacy is the use of headphones.  \r\n\r\nToday, the Director of Engineering walked through my neighborhood looking for someone.  He said something that I couldn't hear through headphones, so I pulled mine off—as did, apparently, most everyone else nearby.  Chuckling, he announced he'd been talking to himself (a frequent occurrence) but that he appreciated the headphones doffed in his honor.  \r\n\r\nBefore striding off, he said, \"It's like a modern kind of salute, shows *respect*, I like it.\"\r\n\r\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments archived-comments\">\r\n            <h3>Archived Comments</h3>\r\n            \r\n        <ul class=\"comments\">\r\n            \r\n        <li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091005\">\r\n            <div class=\"meta\">\r\n                <div class=\"author\">\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=38bd97b8b78bb0926fc0916da9c90641&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"\">MichaelBrianBentley</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <a href=\"#comment-221091005\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T21:47:29\">2005-09-26T21:47:29</time></a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"content\"><p>Headphones make my ears itch in seconds. I haven't found a set that do the job and don't drive me crazy.</p></div>\r\n            \r\n        </li>\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091006\">\r\n            <div class=\"meta\">\r\n                <div class=\"author\">\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://dean.edwards.name/\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=b33181b8e12bd10dfa373acc8af37cbb&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://dean.edwards.name/\">Dean Edwards</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <a href=\"#comment-221091006\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T23:51:42\">2005-09-26T23:51:42</time></a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"content\"><p>You work in Hell.</p></div>\r\n            \r\n        </li>\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091008\">\r\n            <div class=\"meta\">\r\n                <div class=\"author\">\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2377f34a68801b861c3e54e1301f0dce&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://www.decafbad.com\">l.m.orchard</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <a href=\"#comment-221091008\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-26T23:59:38\">2005-09-26T23:59:38</time></a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"content\"><p>Bah, this guy's not <em>really</em> a drill sargeant or anything.  Also, I actually like not having a door and walls—at least so far.</p></div>\r\n            \r\n        </li>\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\"comment\" id=\"comment-221091009\">\r\n            <div class=\"meta\">\r\n                <div class=\"author\">\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar image\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://joga.be\"><img src=\"http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=8e9f4a1fa29a0923f59f3037bbaa824e&amp;size=32&amp;default=http://mediacdn.disqus.com/1320279820/images/noavatar32.png\"/></a>\r\n                    <a class=\"avatar name\" rel=\"nofollow\" \r\n                       href=\"http://joga.be\">Aneel</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <a href=\"#comment-221091009\" class=\"permalink\"><time datetime=\"2005-09-28T19:12:08\">2005-09-28T19:12:08</time></a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"content\"><p>That's <em>fantastic</em>.</p></div>\r\n            \r\n        </li>\r\n    \r\n        </ul>\r\n    \r\n        </div>\r\n    ",
